Intro:
    This code sends out telegram notification when ssh server is logged in

To install:

    1. on telegram open chat with 'BotFather', to create a bot and obtain token
        enter "/start" to BotFather

    2. enter token to bot_config.json

    3. send any message to the bot, then run setup.py (so it remember who to notify)

    4. run setup2.py with sudo (sudo /usr/bin/python3 setup2.py)

To uninstall

    1. run uninstall.py with (sudo /usr/bin/python3 uninstall.py)

    2. delete this directory